// Encrypted resources embedded into DotaFarm.exe.
// Generated/refreshed by CMake pre-build: scripts/encrypt_resource.py reads
// the source files and produces build/embedded/*_encrypted.bin, which RC
// then embeds as RT_RCDATA. payload_loader::LoadEmbeddedResource() decrypts
// at runtime.
//
// Magic vocabulary (matches payload_loader.h):
//   DFDL — DLLs (Andromeda, ProxyHook)             — manual map, no disk
//   DFSP — Spoofer family (spoofer.sys, kdu.exe)   — disk-stage, exec/load

ANDROMEDA_DLL  RCDATA  "embedded/andromeda_encrypted.bin"
PROXYHOOK_DLL  RCDATA  "embedded/proxyhook_encrypted.bin"
SPOOFER_SYS    RCDATA  "embedded/spoofer_encrypted.bin"
KDU_EXE        RCDATA  "embedded/kdu_encrypted.bin"
